<body>
<div><head>王氏喪服要記</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a" ed="CHANT" n="001-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.2">魯哀公祖載其父。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.3">孔子曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.4">「寧設表門乎？」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.5">公曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.6">「不也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.7">夫表門起於禹。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.8">禹治洪水，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.9">故表其門以紀其功。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.10">吾父無功，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.11">何用焉？」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.12">《太平御覽》卷五百四十八。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.13">「寧設菰廬乎？」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.14">公曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.15">「菰廬起太伯。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.16">太伯出奔，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.17">聞古公薨，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.18">還赴喪，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.19">故作菰廬以彰其尸。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.20">吾父無太伯之罪，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.21">何用此為？」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.22">同上。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.23">「寧設五穀囊乎？」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.24">公曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.25">「不也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.26">五穀囊者起於伯夷叔齊讓國，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.27">不食周粟而餓于首陽之山，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.28">恐其魂之餓也，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.29">故作五穀囊。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.30">吾父食味含哺而死，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.31">何用此為？」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.32">歐陽詢《藝文類聚》卷八十五，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.33">《太平御覽》卷七百四。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.34">「寧設挂樹乎？」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.35">公曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.36">「不也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.37">挂樹者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.38">起於介子推。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.39">子推，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.40">晉之人也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.41">文公有內難，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.42">出國之狄，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.43">子推隨其行，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.44">割肉以續軍糧。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.45">後文公復國，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.46">忽忘子推，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.47">子推奉唱而歌，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.48">文公始悟。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.49">當授爵祿，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.50">子推奔介山，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.51">抱木而燒死。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.52">國人葬之，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.53">恐其神魂賈於地，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.54">故作挂樹焉。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.55">吾父生於宮殿，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.56">死於枕席，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.57">何用挂樹為？」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.58">酈道元《水經注》卷六。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.59">「寧設魂衣乎？」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.60">公曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.61">「魂衣起宛荊。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.62">宛荊於山下道逢寒死，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.63">羊角哀迎其屍。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.64">恐神之寒，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.65">故作魂衣。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.66">吾父生服錦繡，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.67">死於衣被，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.68">何用此為？」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.69">《太平御覽》卷八百八十六。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.70">「寧設桐人乎？」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.71">公曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.72">「桐人起於虞卿，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.73">齊人虞卿惡繼母不得養，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.74">父死不得葬。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.75">自知有過，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.76">故作桐人。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.77">吾父生得供養，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.78">何桐人為？」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.79">《太平御覽》卷五百五十二。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.80">「寧設三桃湯乎？」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.81">公曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.82">「不也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.83">桃湯起於衛，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.84">靈公有女嫁楚，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.85">乳母送之。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.86">道聞夫死，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.87">欲將新婦還。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.88">婦曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.89">『女有三從，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.90">今屬於人，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.91">死當卒哀。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.92">因素車白馬，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.93">進到夫家，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.94">治三桃湯，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.95">以沐死音。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.96">出東北隅，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.97">禮三終，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.98">使死者不恨。』<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.99">吾父無所恨，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.100">何用桃湯焉？」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.101">《太平御覽》卷九百六十七。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.102">案：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.103">諸書散引首皆有「魯哀公祖載其父孔子曰」或作「魯哀公葬父，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.104">孔子問曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.105">家宛斯先生。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.106">《繹史》卷八十六孔子類記刪合訂為一篇，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.107">茲據錄之，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.108">間有脫字，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-1a.109">依原引補。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-2a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-2a" ed="CHANT" n="001-2a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-2a.2">別子為祖，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-2a.3">諸侯母弟則不盡為祖矣。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-2a.4">杜佑《通典》卷七十三「傅純問賀循喪服要記」云云引王氏。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-2a.5">禮有親喪而君來弔，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-2a.6">則免絰，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-2a.7">貫左臂，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-2a.8">去杖，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-2a.9">迎拜于大門之外，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-2a.10">見馬首，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-2a.11">不哭，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-2a.12">先入門右，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-2a.13">庭中北面。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-2a.14">君升自東階，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-2a.15">南面哭，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-2a.16">主人乃哭。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-2a.17">君出，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-2a.18">又拜送大門外。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-2a.19">《通典》卷八十三。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-3a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-3a" ed="CHANT" n="001-3a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-3a.2">按禮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-3a.3">三年之喪，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-3a.4">終服不弔。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-3a.5">期之喪，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-3a.6">既練而弔。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-3a.7">大功之喪，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-3a.8">既葬而弔。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-3a.9">同上。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-3a.10">老疾三諫去者為舊君服𪗋，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-3a.11">《通典》卷九十引王肅、賀循，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-3a.12">又云「王賀要記」。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-4a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-4a" ed="CHANT" n="001-4a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-4a.2">庶子服出母：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-4a.3">「父在服𪗋縗周，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-4a.4">父沒不服。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-4a.5">《通典》卷九十四殷仲堪引王賀首句據殷補。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-4a.6">為出繼母無服。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-4a.7">季祖鍾云：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-4a.8">繼母在，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-4a.9">如母；<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-4a.10">出則為父所去，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-4a.11">不服也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-4a.12">《通典》卷九十四引王肅首句，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-4a.13">據補。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-5a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-5a" ed="CHANT" n="001-5a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-5a.2">周則沒閏。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-5a.3">《通典》卷一百王儉引鄭射、王賀。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-5a.4">禮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-5a.5">師弟子無服，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-5a.6">以弔服加麻臨之，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-5a.7">哭之於寢。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-5a.8">《通典》卷一百一。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-6a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-6a" ed="CHANT" n="001-6a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-6a.2">司徒文子改葬，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-6a.3">其叔父間服於子思。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-6a.4">子思曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-6a.5">「禮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-6a.6">父母改葬，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-6a.7">緦而除，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-6a.8">不忍無服送至親也。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-6a.9">本有三年之服者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-6a.10">道有遠近，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-6a.11">或有艱故，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-6a.12">既葬而除，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-6a.13">不待有三月之服也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-6a.14">非父母，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-6a.15">無服，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-6a.16">無服則弔服加麻。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-6a.17">《通典》卷一百二。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-7a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-7a" ed="CHANT" n="001-7a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-7a.2">有小功喪服，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-7a.3">改葬父母，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-7a.4">宜服改葬緦，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-7a.5">卒事反故服。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-7a.6">同上。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-7a.7">上句據《通典》補。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-7a.8">改葬緦，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-7a.9">既虞而除之。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-7a.10">同上。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-8a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-8a" ed="CHANT" n="001-8a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-8a.2">棺毀見屍，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-8a.3">痛之極也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-8a.4">今遇賊見毀，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-8a.5">理無輕重也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-8a.6">同上引鄭康成、王子雍。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-8a.7">斬縗之喪未葬，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-8a.8">主喪不徐。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1080_CHANT_001-8a.9">《通典》卷一百三宋蔡廓問雷次宗引王肅。<lb/></seg>
</p>
</div>
</body>
